        "question": "Given \\(f(x) = x^2 + 3x\\), find \\(f(x+h)\\)",
        "options": [
          "\\(x^2 + 2xh + h^2 + 3x + 3h\\)",
          "\\(x^2 + 2xh + 3x + 3h\\)",
          "\\(x^2 + 2xh + h^2 + 3x\\)",
          "\\(2xh + h^2 + 3h\\)"
        ],
        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "f(x+h) = (x+h)^2 + 3(x+h) = x^2 + 2xh + h^2 + 3x + 3h"
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "Compute \\(f(x+h) - f(x)\\) for \\(f(x) = x^2 + 3x\\)",
