          "\\(h^2 + 3h\\)"
        ],
        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "f(x+h) - f(x) = (x^2 + 2xh + h^2 + 3x + 3h) - (x^2 + 3x) = 2xh + h^2 + 3h"
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
