          "\\(2x + 3\\)",
          "\\(2x + h\\)",
          "\\(x + h + 3\\)"
        ],
        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "[f(x+h)-f(x)]/h = (2xh + h^2 + 3h)/h = 2x + h + 3"
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "Find \\(f'(x)\\) using first principles for \\(f(x) = x^2 + 3x\\)",
